130
00:11:35,033 --> 00:11:35,092
8,50.

131
00:11:35,113 --> 00:11:35,613
Det går inte billigare.

132
00:11:35,633 --> 00:11:35,852
Älskling.

133
00:11:35,893 --> 00:11:36,013
Torsk!

134
00:11:36,033 --> 00:11:36,953
Ja, och den är nyfiskad i morse.

135
00:11:36,974 --> 00:11:37,433
Jag tror jag donar.

136
00:11:37,494 --> 00:11:37,754
En ambulans.

137
00:11:37,774 --> 00:11:38,333
Men kör inte fort.

138
00:11:38,375 --> 00:11:38,794
Lova mig det.

139
00:11:38,815 --> 00:11:39,195
Förbannade telefon.
